{"tid":1706521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一定要令股市癱瘓才可對政權造成最大傷害, 點解一直無人朝這個方向諗","createTime":"2019-11-11T06:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T15:08:58.000Z","uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"849262cbbec496961e5c6ce53893ddc70718ebd0","tid":1706521,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:09:18.000Z","msg":"現時任何方法包括和理非同勇武對政權傷害都係有限, 就算搞得成罷工, 或者勇武再升級暴力, 亦唔見得令政權害怕。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有令股市癱瘓才可重創政權, 一來經濟真係會好大影響(而家呢D影響算得咩); 二來香港股市六成係中資, 中國無可能唔緊張; 三來香港係國際金融中心, 會影響環球, 國際必然高度關注</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這個才是政權的春袋, 攻入禮賓府/政總/警總都無咁大效力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">聽日開始要癱瘓港交所, 唔好比股市開得成</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d766b353a97c85be36a6df7869b0d7ddfd61a071","tid":1706521,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"引狗無差別襲擊準時返工打工仔，以後無人返工了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ca4f86a5f29c6bdf174e91349e1294b0b1f0e57","tid":1706521,"uid":5591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"叫誠哥沽爆佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee63092b76294feb831ed0cfcf20cb89074f8d3","tid":1706521,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ca4f86a5f29c6bdf174e91349e1294b0b1f0e57","tid":1706521,"uid":5591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"叫誠哥沽爆佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"沽爆無用, 係要令股市停止運作"},{"pid":"c0cbca80ff1c3506c9dcaab1b863396719b1b0a3","tid":1706521,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"715ba039c7fd